{"tid":1165579,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Disney+ 正在籌備《真實謊言》劇集","createTime":"2019-05-22T01:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T13:39:41.000Z","uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"42f4851aa534a90a170f8f1d2a41cfb583a9156e","tid":1165579,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T01:28:01.000Z","msg":"美國導演 McG 在 2000 年初接連帶來了兩部《神探俏嬌娃》（Charlie&rsquo;s Angel）電影後，於 2009 年接手執導了第四部《未來戰士》（Terminator Salvation），而在十年之後，McG 又將再一次把導演James Cameron與Arnold Schwarzenegger合作的代表作之一重新呈現給觀眾。<br />\n<br />\nMcG 日前在接受 Collider 訪問時透露，正在為迪士尼影業的串流影音平台 Disney+ 籌備《真實謊言》（True Lies）的影集改編；此外，McG 也表示，一直以來James Cameron都對他很好，也很支持他，因此這一次能有他的祝福來進行電視重啟對他來說是很重要的。<br />\n<br />\n至於《真實謊言》影集現在的進度為何，McG 表示他才剛構思好了故事大綱，正要進行下一步的動作，並且將在接下來的這個夏天開始著手劇本；而 McG 近期的執導作品包括《辣手保姆》（The Babysitter）以及即將在本週末上線的《地球邊緣》（Rim of the World），兩部皆為 Netflix 電影。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hypesphere.com/news/16681\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hypesphere.com%2Fnews%2F16681&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TaP8PJJZD286lWcuKEclkJo%3D&h=943cbbcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hypesphere.com/news/16681</a>"},{"pid":"271c7ce01d7e42b8e902e1076d54631f38b965b6","tid":1165579,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T01:33:18.000Z","msg":"阿諾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f360482fc97fa5c9c0fdd2433e6173f25eacb86e","tid":1165579,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:34:43.000Z","msg":"Terminator Salvation<br />\n都幾垃圾吓"},{"pid":"07d818f9b2ef938e249ed12a0386d17c34e958f3","tid":1165579,"uid":42848,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/W6jPgE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.g